    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807700/extras/49f1df683b33f6202dfe9a26ac10bdc4.poster.avif?t=1724978433\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807700/extras/49f1df683b33f6202dfe9a26ac10bdc4.webm?t=1724978433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807700/extras/49f1df683b33f6202dfe9a26ac10bdc4.mp4?t=1724978433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2></strong><br>&quot;End Of Legends&quot; is a blend of roguelike deck-building and auto battler mechanics. Assume the mantle of a forsaken Dark Lord, rising from the shadows to exact retribution upon humanity for its transgressions. Harness the dark arts to cast devastating spells, summon malevolent minions, and dismantle those who dared cross you. As you navigate through this merciless world, your strategic prowess will be the key to your dominion or downfall.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807700/extras/5b4fc50ecb310433c34a19859d781465.poster.avif?t=1724978433\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807700/extras/5b4fc50ecb310433c34a19859d781465.webm?t=1724978433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807700/extras/5b4fc50ecb310433c34a19859d781465.mp4?t=1724978433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring:</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dynamic upgrades that evolve your gameplay, ensuring each battle is filled with new strategies and outcomes.<br></li><li>Unique storytelling through grimoire cards, revealing the Dark Lord's past and influencing your abilities with crucial choices.<br></li><li>Epic battles against thousands of enemies, challenging your tactics and the might of your summoned armies.<br></li><li>Grand spells that unleash catastrophic destruction, turning the tide of combat with awe-inspiring power.</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807700/extras/54df4f89af7501646899c68e645200bb.poster.avif?t=1724978433\" width=394 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807700/extras/54df4f89af7501646899c68e645200bb.webm?t=1724978433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807700/extras/54df4f89af7501646899c68e645200bb.mp4?t=1724978433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cruel world:</h2></strong><br>An array of unique enemies and bosses, each presenting their own deadly arsenals and minions to test your cunning and resolve.<br>In &quot;End Of Legends,&quot; the world teeters on the brink of despair, its fate intertwined with the whims of a figure shrouded in vengeance. Each grimoire card unveils a piece of the past, a story of betrayal, and a path to power untold. Your decisions within these memories forge your legacy, offering unparalleled power or unforeseen consequences. Will you reclaim your lost honor and rewrite the annals of history, or will you plunge the world further into darkness? The choice is yours, Dark Lord.",
